==English==
===Etymology===
From [[w:Friedrich Paschen|Friedrich Paschen]] and [[w:Ernst Emil Alexander Back|Ernst Emil Alexander Back]] German physicists
===Noun===
'''[[Paschen]]-[[Back]] [[effect]]'''
#{{physics}} a form of the [[Zeeman effect]] that affects the [[spectral line]]s obtained when a light source is placed in a very strong [[magnetic field]]

